  - m_Id: 6869958365184
    m_Localized: 'You discover the iron Meteor !


      the iron meteor give iron
      in rapport of the forge reward, But they are relativlty rare.


      Once
      you destroy it you can collect the iron in the space.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6872076488704
    m_Localized: "You discover the uranium Meteor ! \n\nthe iron meteor give uranium
      in rapport of the forge reward, But they are relativlty rare.\n\n Once you
      destroy it you can collect the uranium in the space."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6876887355392
    m_Localized: 'you unlock the rocket


      the rocket target the strongest meteor
      and deal massive damage.


      if a rocket destroy a spillter meteor,  its
      children will not spawn.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
