  - m_Id: 52837399498752
    m_Localized: 'You discover the diamand Meteor !


      The diamand meteor give
      1 diamand, but it''s extremly rare.


      It is smaller, faster, and has
      more health, nut does not deal damage to the spaceship.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52843292495872
    m_Localized: 'You discover the reinforcer Meteor !


      The reinforced meteor
      has more health, but it is slower.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52841463779328
    m_Localized: "You discover the splitter Meteor ! \n\nWhen destroyed, the splitter
      meteor spawn two smaller meteors. \n\nThe smaller meteors do not give xp."
